## 🎯 **Technical Details**

**Files Modified**:
- `index-complete.html` - Replaced Tailwind @apply with explicit CSS

**CSS Changes**:
- Removed dependency on Tailwind utility classes
- Added explicit background-color, color, border properties
- Enhanced focus states with orange accent
- Improved placeholder text styling

**Color Scheme**:
```css
/* Light Mode */
Background: #ffffff (white)
Text: #1f2937 (dark gray)
Border: #d1d5db (light gray)  
Placeholder: #6b7280 (medium gray)
Focus: #ff6500 (orange)

/* Dark Mode */
Background: #1f2937 (dark gray)
Text: #ffffff (white)
Border: #4b5563 (darker gray)
Placeholder: #9ca3af (light gray)
Focus: #ff6500 (orange)
```

**Browser Support**:
- Chrome ✅ (Tested)
- Firefox ✅ (Expected to work)
- Safari ✅ (Expected to work)
- Edge ✅ (Expected to work)

